      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. It remains a functional daily driver, but it shows clear signs of age and use. The engine and transmission are operational, though there are minor oil seeps and the suspension is beginning to feel worn. Cosmetically, the car has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger side, while the interior shows some staining and wear on the seats. It is a solid budget-friendly option for someone willing to put in a little work or looking for basic transportation.",
