    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family. It looks and drives exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found! If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
